# HSM collector conformance v1.
# Format: case|action|arg1|arg2|arg3|arg4
# Supported actions:
# create_collector
# start
# stop
# create_int_sensor|path
# create_bool_sensor|path
# create_double_sensor|path
# create_string_sensor|path
# create_enum_sensor|path
# create_last_int_sensor|path|default_value
# create_last_bool_sensor|path|default_value
# create_last_double_sensor|path|default_value
# create_last_string_sensor|path|default_value
# create_int_sensors|count|path_prefix
# create_mixed_instant_sensors|count|path_prefix
# add_int|sensor_index|value|status|comment
# add_bool|sensor_index|value|status|comment
# add_double|sensor_index|value|status|comment
# add_string|sensor_index|value|status|comment
# add_enum|sensor_index|value|status|comment
# add_int_sequence|sensor_count|values_per_sensor|start_value|status|comment
# add_int_parallel|worker_count|values_per_worker|sensor_count|status|comment
# add_mixed_instant_sequence|set_count|values_per_set|start_value|status|comment
# add_mixed_instant_parallel|worker_count|values_per_worker|set_count|status|comment
# expect_conflicting_mixed_creates_rejected_parallel|worker_count|path_count|path_prefix
# repeat_start_stop_add|cycles|sensor_index|status|comment_prefix
# expect_sent_count|count|optional_timeout_seconds
# expect_payload_contains|payload_index|substring
# expect_comment_length|payload_index|length
# expect_all_payloads_contain|substring
# expect_payload_value_sequence|start_payload_index|count|start_value
# expect_payload_type_counts|bool_count|int_count|double_count|string_count|enum_count

before_start_drops_value|create_collector
before_start_drops_value|create_int_sensor|contract/int
before_start_drops_value|add_int|0|7|Ok|before start
before_start_drops_value|expect_sent_count|0

running_collector_stores_int_payload|create_collector
running_collector_stores_int_payload|create_int_sensor|contract/int
running_collector_stores_int_payload|start
running_collector_stores_int_payload|add_int|0|42|Warning|watch
running_collector_stores_int_payload|expect_sent_count|1
running_collector_stores_int_payload|expect_payload_contains|0|"Type":1
running_collector_stores_int_payload|expect_payload_contains|0|"Path":"conformance-host/conformance-module/contract/int"
running_collector_stores_int_payload|expect_payload_contains|0|"Value":42
running_collector_stores_int_payload|expect_payload_contains|0|"Status":2
running_collector_stores_int_payload|expect_payload_contains|0|"Comment":"watch"

stop_drops_late_values|create_collector
stop_drops_late_values|create_int_sensor|contract/stop
stop_drops_late_values|start
stop_drops_late_values|add_int|0|1|Ok|sent
stop_drops_late_values|expect_sent_count|1
stop_drops_late_values|stop
stop_drops_late_values|add_int|0|2|Ok|dropped
stop_drops_late_values|expect_sent_count|1

duplicate_sensor_path_is_idempotent|create_collector
duplicate_sensor_path_is_idempotent|create_int_sensor|contract/duplicate
duplicate_sensor_path_is_idempotent|create_int_sensor|contract/duplicate
duplicate_sensor_path_is_idempotent|start
duplicate_sensor_path_is_idempotent|add_int|0|1|Ok|first
duplicate_sensor_path_is_idempotent|add_int|1|2|Ok|second
duplicate_sensor_path_is_idempotent|expect_sent_count|2
duplicate_sensor_path_is_idempotent|expect_payload_contains|0|"Path":"conformance-host/conformance-module/contract/duplicate"
duplicate_sensor_path_is_idempotent|expect_payload_contains|1|"Path":"conformance-host/conformance-module/contract/duplicate"

long_comment_is_trimmed|create_collector
long_comment_is_trimmed|create_int_sensor|contract/comment
long_comment_is_trimmed|start
long_comment_is_trimmed|add_int|0|1|Ok|repeat:a:1100
long_comment_is_trimmed|expect_sent_count|1
long_comment_is_trimmed|expect_comment_length|0|1024
